ound_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Ship Building\";s:4:\"text\";s:672:\"<p><strong>We specialise in, Offshore Vessels </strong>which are specially designed ships for transporting goods and personnel to offshore <strong>oil platform </strong>that operate deep in oceans.  The size of these vessels ranges between 20 meters and 100 meters. They are good at accomplishing a variety of tasks in the supply chain. The category may include<strong> Platform Supply Vessels (PSV), offshore barges, </strong>and all types of specialty vessels including <strong>Anchor Handling Vessels, Drilling Vessels, Well Intervention Vessels, Ice Breaking Vessels, Cable Laying Vessels, Seismic Vessels, </strong>and <strong>Fire Fighting Vessels</strong>.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:219:\"<p><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/home/ship-repairs/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/maintenance.jpeg\" alt=\"maintenance\" width=\"227\" height=\"222\" /></a></p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"Ship Repair\";s:4:\"text\";s:531:\"<p>Full dry docking services, voyage repairs, conversions and upgrades, new buildings, riding squads, specialist marine spares &amp; services, and design and engineering capabilities.</p><p>We have undertaken a number of ship repair assignments in India. This include the work we have done for all major ship yards in India, including Goad shipyard and Bharti Shipyard.</p><p>There specialisation have given us focused strength to develop, indigenous technology on the front which only scales to magnificent level of efficeincy</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:248:\"<p><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/home/manpower-support/\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-23\" src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Computer-Repair-Main-Icon-300x300.png\" alt=\"Computer-Repair-Main-Icon\" width=\"247\" height=\"247\" /></a></p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:2;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:4;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"Manpower Support\";s:4:\"text\";s:577:\"We have specialised set of welder, fitters, plumbers, who have been certified by the Indian govt. These professional have had over 15 year experience each, in the chosen field of engineering.\n\nOur present staff strength, includes 5 design engineers, 25 structural welder, 15 Sheet metal welder, 15 tradesmen, 45 life support staff.\n\nThis trade allows them to earn a good living which supporting their families and group member.\n\nWe currently have more than 250 works deployed at various client locations.<a href=\"http://shiptech.in/home-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Manpower Support</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:2;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:5;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:2;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s