text\";s:1390:\"<p>With over 25 years in the Shipping Industry, Shiptech is regarded has a specialist in hull fabrication and hull erection work. We have been rated as the number, one ship building by by all our clients.</p><p>We specialise in hull and fabrication work and have in the past taken up several complicated design work.</p><p>We presently have prestigious clients like GOA Shipyard, Hindustan Shipyard, L&amp;T shipping, Bharati Shipyard, and Tebma Shipyard, all of whom, have empanelled us on our merit.</p><p>Mr Prashata Karar with over 40 year experience in the Industry is regarded one of the finest Naval Architects by the industry. He has in the past, single handedly managed to solve several complicated design elements which were presented to him.</p><p>We have in past built, ships for the Indian Navy, Platform supply vessels, STS Vessels, Tugs, Pilot Ships, Mooring Vessels, Dredger vessels, Barges, Passenger Ships, Cargo Vessels and Fugro Vessels.</p><p>Presently we are building and OPV and floating dry dock for L&amp;T shipping in Kattupalli, Chennai, India.</p><p>With over 200 workers specialised in Fabrication, erection, gas cutting, grinding &amp; welding, and dry survey we can boast of a formidable team of technicians in our group.</p><p>We also have ability to quickly scale, by drawing into a pool of resources, who will gladly come to work for Shiptech</p><p> </p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"573819d474ed0\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:240:\"<p><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/drawing.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-151\" src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/drawing-300x185.jpg