ard.</p><p>There specialisation have given us focused strength to develop, indigenous technology on the front which only scales to magnificent level of efficeincy</p><p><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Computer-Repair-Main-Icon.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-23\" src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Computer-Repair-Main-Icon-300x300.png\" alt=\"Computer-Repair-Main-Icon\" width=\"168\" height=\"168\"></a></p><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Manpower Support</h3><p>We have specialised set of welder, fitters, plumbers, who have been certified by the Indian govt. These professional have had over 15 year experience each, in the chosen field of engineering.</p><p>Our present staff strength, includes 5 design engineers, 25 structural welder, 15 Sheet metal welder, 15 tradesmen, 45 life support staff.</p><p>This trade allows them to earn a good living which supporting their families and group member.</p><p>We currently have more than 250 works deployed at various client locations.</p>','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-03 10:22:23','2016-05-03 10:22:23','',7,'http://shiptech.in/2016/05/03/7-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(74,1,'2016-05-03 09:35:44','2016-05-03 09:35:44','<a href=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/ship-building-e1462180393272.jpg\"><img src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/ship-building-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"ship building\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-24\"></a><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/photo-1445020388347-f82531617735.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/photo-1445020388347-f82531617735-300x200.jpeg\" alt=\"photo-1445020388347-f82531617735\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15\"></a><a href=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/photo-1420496401585-7f22ce8b8b8a.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://shiptech.in/wp-content/up